                ft.Text(
                    "2.National Child Labour Project Scheme",
                    size=20,
                    weight=ft.FontWeight.W600,
                    color="#000000"
                ),
                ft.Image(
                    src="assets/Screenshot (80).png",
                    width=384,
                    height=245,
                    fit=ft.ImageFit.COVER
                ),
                ft.Text(
                    "The National Child Labour Project (NCLP) Scheme is a significant initiative launched by the Government of India to combat child labor, particularly in hazardous industries, and to ensure that children who are working are provided with education, rehabilitation, and a secure future. It aims to withdraw children from work and mainstream them into the educational system, while simultaneously providing them with vocational training to help them build a better future.By providing education, vocational training, and rehabilitation for rescued child laborers, the scheme aims to eradicate child labor and promote the well-being and future prospects of children.",
                    size=15,
